A coworker from Tartărăşi said he didn't get his money and he has to go by bus.
Let's not be hypocrites.
There's little money.
Sometimes I'm ashamed to pick up money from the cash register.
At the end of my term of office, I'll report on everything I've spent, other than the salaries of the cabinet employees and their maintenance.
